"Mall Crawl" by Kristen

Release along with the "Quixe" interpreter.

The player is in the Hallway.

[Variables]
The timeToEscape is a number variable. The timeToEscape is 30.

[Rooms and Layout]
The Hallway is a room.
Justice is a room.
Sears is a room.
Forever 21 is a room.
Auntie Anne's is a room.
Brooks Brothers is a room.

Auntie Anne's door is a locked door. Auntie Anne's door is north of the hallway.
Auntie Anne's is north of Auntie Anne's door.
Justice is south of the hallway and north of Brooks Brothers.
Sears is east of the hallway.
Forever 21 is west of the hallway.
Brooks Brothers is south of Justice.

[Hallway]
The description of the Hallway is "You are on the ground floor of the mall, exploring. You see the food court in front of you to the North and some stores around you."

[Auntie Anne's]
The description of Auntie Anne's is "It's just a run down pretzel shop."
The grill is a fixed in place thing in Auntie Anne's. The grill is a supporter.
The moldy pretzel is a thing. "There is a moldy pretzel on the grill. Only the most hungry would dare touch that." The moldy pretzel is on the grill.

[Justice]
The description of Justice is "You've never seen an abandoned store with so many clothes! Justice has remained pristine despite years of going untouched. Maybe it's all the sparkles? Justice is next to Brooks Brothers."
The clothes rack is a container in Justice. 
The jacket is a thing. It is inside the clothes rack. An openable container called the jacket pocket is part of the jacket. In the jacket pocket is a receipt.
The description of the jacket is "It is a normal girl's jacket. Definitely wouldn't fit you and too many sparkles. It has two pockets, a hood, and is rather plush."
The description of the receipt is "It is a crumpled up old receipt, but it seems to have something written on it."

[Forever 21]
The description of Forever 21 is "No wonder it went bankrupt! Way too many shirts about tacos litter the ground."
The clothes shelf is a container in Forever 21.
The taco shirt is a thing. It is inside the clothes shelf. The description of the taco shirt is "It is just a plain red shirt with the word tacos on it."
The directory is a thing. It is inside the clothes rack. The description of the directory is "There is a large red circle around the food court. I wonder what that means."

[Sears]
The description of Sears is "It is a large, vacant department store. You can't believe this used to be America's department store. You wander around, but there's nothing on the shelves. It's a ghost town."

[Brooks Brothers]
The description of Brooks Brothers is "You can't believe such a high end store died in a mall like this. You hope that there is clothes leftover, maybe you can take them and re-sell them on Depop."



